<H3> Software Architecture </H3>
<UL>

<P><LI>
<A HREF="http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?coll=GUIDE&dl=GUIDE&id=225042">
A Component- and Message-Based Architectural Style for GUI
Software</A>, by Richard N. Taylor, Nenad Medvidovic, Kenneth M. Anderson,
E. James Whitehead Jr., Jason E. Robbins, Kari A. Nies, Peyman Oreizy,
and Deborah L. Dubrow, <i>IEEE Transactions on Software Engineering</i>,
vol. 22, no. 6, pages 390-406, June 1996.
</UL>

<HR>
<H3> User Interface </H3>
<UL>

<P><LI>
<A HREF="http://doi.acm.org/10.1145/210181.210182">
Chiron-1: A Software Architecture for User Interface Development,
Maintenance, and Run-time Support</A>,
by Richard N. Taylor, Kari A. Nies, Gregory Alan Bolcer, Craig A. MacFarlane,
Gregory F. Johnson, and Kenneth M. Anderson in
<i> ACM Transactions on Computer-Human Interaction,</i> 2(2):105-144, June 1995.
<A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/Arcadia/arcadia_papers/ui/TOCHI_abstract.html"> Abstract </A>
<P>
<LI>
<A HREF="http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.57.4407&rep=rep1&type=pdf">
Supporting Separations of Concerns and Concurrency in the Chiron-1  User Interface System</A>,
by Richard N. Taylor, Kari A. Nies, Gregory Alan Bolcer, Craig A. MacFarlane,
Gregory F. Johnson, and Kenneth M. Anderson in <i> UCI Technical Report UCI-94-12.</i>
  
  <P>
<LI>
<b>A Software Engineering Approach to User Interface Management Systems</b>,
by Richard N. Taylor and Kari A. Forester in
<i>CrossTalk, The Journal of Defense Software Engineering</i>, Dec 1993.
<A HREF="http:/~kari/papers/crosstalk.html"> Abstract </A>

<P><LI>
<A HREF="papers/chiron.1.4_user_manual.pdf">
Chiron-1 User Manual, v1.4</A>,
by Kari A. Nies, Craig MacFarlane, Mary Cameron, and Gregory Bolcer in
<i> Arcadia Document UCI-93-07.</i>
<A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/Arcadia/arcadia_papers/ui/user_manual_abstract.html"> Abstract </A>

<P><LI>
<A HREF="papers/chiron.1.4_client_design.pdf">
Chiron 1.4 Client Design</A>,
by Kari A. Nies in
<i> Arcadia Document UCI-93-02.</i>
<A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/Arcadia/arcadia_papers/ui/client_abstract.html"> Abstract </A>

<P><LI>
<b>Aplication of Chiron-1 Concepts to Guidance and Control Systems</b>, by Richard N. Taylor and Kari A. Forester
 in <em>Joint Services Guidance & Control Committe (JSGCC0/DARPA) Software Initiative Workshop</em>, Vail, CO, Nov 1992.
</UL>

